Title: Embassies and Envoys
Description:
I feared what we would find when we returned here, but I am proud to see that though we were forced to leave, you were able to forge a friendship with the earthen and stand against the nerubians.

With your strength, we will win this. But first we need a plan, and for that we need space here in Dornogal for discussion.
ObjectivesText: Setup your faction's embassy in Dornogal.
ObjectivesCompletionText: Find Moira in Dornogal and report back

Objectives.Text: Horde Embassy steward found in Dornogal
